Environment: Next.js 16 App Router PWA at mrp.meavo.app. Satellite app of meavo-gateway on the shared Neon Postgres. NOT the legacy Supabase invoice scanner (see docs/archive-invoice-scanner.md).

## Stack

- Next.js 16 App Router, TypeScript strict, React 19 вАФ **webpack forced** (`--webpack`; Serwist PWA is incompatible with Turbopack)
- Tailwind CSS 4 + shadcn/ui (Radix primitives) in `src/components/ui/` вАФ approved org deviation
- Prisma 6 via `@meavo/db` (github tag) вЖТ shared Neon Postgres; schema at `node_modules/@meavo/db/prisma/schema.prisma`
- NextAuth v5 JWT, Google SSO only, invite-only via gateway `ToolCardAccess` (`MRP_TOOL_CARD_ID`)
- `next-intl` вАФ locales `bg` (default) + `en`, all routes under `src/app/[locale]/`
- `@google/genai` (Gemini) extraction, Vercel Blob storage, Serwist service worker (`src/sw.ts`)
- pnpm 9+, Node 22+, Vercel `fra1`

## Do NOT

- Edit the Prisma schema here вАФ it lives in meavo-db; bump the `@meavo/db` git tag instead
- Run `prisma db push` вАФ shared DB; script intentionally disabled
- Write stock quantities directly вАФ go through `applyMovement()` in `src/lib/stock/movements.ts`
- Call Zeron adapters directly вАФ use `enqueueZeronSync()` (`src/lib/zeron/queue.ts`)
- Hardcode UI strings вАФ use `next-intl` messages (`messages/bg.json` + `messages/en.json`)
- Skip `requireApiUser()` in API routes вАФ middleware excludes `/api/*`
- Expose raw Vercel Blob URLs вАФ stream originals via `/api/documents/[id]/file`
- Switch dev/build to Turbopack
- Commit secrets or `.env.local`

## Code layout

| Area | Path |
|------|------|
| Pages (locale-prefixed, auth via `(app)` group) | `src/app/[locale]/(app)/`, login at `src/app/[locale]/login/` |
| API route handlers (primary mutation pattern вАФ no Server Actions) | `src/app/api/` |
| Domain logic | `src/lib/stock/`, `src/lib/documents/`, `src/lib/extractor/`, `src/lib/import/`, `src/lib/suppliers/`, `src/lib/learning/` |
| Integrations | `src/lib/zeron/` (ERP), `src/lib/sheets/` + `src/lib/google/` (Sheets), `src/lib/storage/` (Blob) |
| Auth | `src/lib/auth.ts`, `src/lib/auth/session.ts`, `src/lib/api/guard.ts`, `src/middleware.ts` |
| i18n | `src/i18n/`, `messages/` |
| Tests | N/A вАФ `pnpm lint` + `pnpm typecheck` only |

## Data flow

```
Browser (PWA) вФАвФАfetchвФАвФАвЦґ /api/* route вФАвФАвЦґ src/lib/* вФАвФАвЦґ Prisma вФАвФАвЦґ shared Neon Postgres
                                             вФВ
                                             вФЬвФАвЦґ enqueueZeronSync() вФАвЦґ Zeron adapter (stub/export/api/agent) + MrpSyncAttempt audit
                                             вФЬвФАвЦґ Gemini extraction (src/lib/extractor) вЧАвФА supplier hints (src/lib/learning)
                                             вФФвФАвЦґ Vercel Blob (originals)
Vercel cron (0 */2 * * *) вФАвЦґ /api/sheets/sync вФАвЦґ runSheetSync() вЧАвФА Google Sheets (batches) вФАвЦґ stock deductions via applyMovement()
```

Every stock quantity change must be an `applyMovement()` call (writes `MrpStockMovement` ledger + updates `MrpStockBalance` cache). Every document approval that should reach Zeron must call `enqueueZeronSync()`.

